<p>To ensure the confidentiality of audit findings, Ripple takes several measures. They restrict access to the findings to authorized personnel only, implement secure communication channels, and enforce strict non-disclosure agreements with all parties involved.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">How Does Ripple Respond to Any Security Vulnerabilities Identified During the Audits?</h3>



<p>During the audits, Ripple responds promptly to any security vulnerabilities identified. They take immediate action to address and fix the vulnerabilities, ensuring the safety and integrity of their platform.</p>



