<ol>
<li><strong>Real-time transaction monitoring:</strong> Utilize advanced monitoring tools to track transactions and identify suspicious patterns or anomalies. This can help you detect potential fraudulent activities and take immediate action.</li>



<li><strong>User behavior analysis: </strong>Analyze user behavior and establish baseline patterns to identify any deviations or unusual activities. This can help you detect unauthorized access attempts or account takeovers.</li>



